Have Background allows you to display a random backround on every page. You can also set specific pages to show only a particular background.

This is a work in progress and has not been tested 100%. Please report any bugs at https://github.com/haveboard/Have-Background

Includes "Color picker" & "Supersized"

	Supersized - Fullscreen Slideshow jQuery Plugin
		Author	: Sam Dunn
		http://www.buildinternet.com/project/supersized		
		www.onemightyroar.com

 	Color picker
		Author: Stefan Petre www.eyecon.ro
		http://www.eyecon.ro/colorpicker/
 
